1. In sublime text, install package ANSIescape
2. depending on your OS, do...

macosx:
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.sublime-syntax ~/Library/Application\ Support/Sublime\ Text\ 3/Packages/User/
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.tmPreferences ~/Library/Application\ Support/Sublime\ Text\ 3/Packages/User/
cp editor_modes/sublime/Make-color.sublime-build ~/Library/Application\ Support/Sublime\ Text\ 3/Packages/User/

linux (ubuntu):
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.sublime-syntax ~/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.tmPreferences ~/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/
cp editor_modes/sublime/Make-color.sublime-build ~/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/

Windows:
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.sublime-syntax C:\Users\<USER NAME>\AppData\Roaming\Sublime Text 3\Packages\User\
cp editor_modes/sublime/smala.tmPreferences C:\Users\<USER NAME>\AppData\Roaming\Sublime Text 3\Packages\User\
cp editor_modes/sublime/Make-color.sublime-build C:\Users\<USER NAME>\AppData\Roaming\Sublime Text 3\Packages\User\